  "id": "RAW_aaab40d0",
  "title": "阿里云联合上海交大荣膺 FAST'26 最佳论文：揭秘云上本地存储的演进与未来发展",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg4NTczNzg2OA==&mid=2247509188&idx=1&sn=13d89ea9e6fad38c1ccc3adb8dafb0f4",
  "date": "2026-03-06 00:31:00",
  "author": "阿里技术",
  "siteName": "阿里技术",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, PingFangSC-regular, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:flex;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;align-items:center;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 0px 10px;padding: 0px 10px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 13px;line-height: 1.75;font-weight: bold;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mf0sc4my175o\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(128, 128, 128);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">这是</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">2026</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(128, 128, 128);visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">年的第<span textstyle=\"\">9</span></span></span></span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(128, 128, 128);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">篇文章</span></span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;color: grey;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0sc4my216h\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">（ 本文阅读时间：10分钟 ）</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-lake-id=\"a20d224c568e48b9d67847a2c66a8c01_p_0\" style=\"margin: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mmd2fnp1xad\" style=\"font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;\">在刚刚结束的存储领域顶级学术会议 FAST '26（24th USENIX Conference on File and Storage Technologies） 上，阿里云（Alibaba &nbsp;Cloud）联合上海交通大学（SJTU）、Solidigm 共同发表的论文 《Here, There and Everywhere: The Past, the Present and the Future of Local Storage in Cloud》 获得</span><strong><span data-spm-anchor-id=\"a2c6h.12873639.article-detail.i0.31b46132h9i2Py\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">最佳论文奖（Best Paper Award）</span></span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;\">。本界大会仅有两篇论文获此殊荣。值得一提的是，这也是阿里云存储相关研究在过去四年内第三次获得国际学术届的最高荣誉。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-lake-id=\"aa1099dadae66ef69b677dbb306c3cde\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span data-card-type=\"inline\" data-lake-card=\"image\" data-card-value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fucc.alicdn.com%2Fpic%2Fdeveloper-ecology%2Fnlekadieflg4i_79dad382a3ed4f3f87ab252da61f2f8a.png%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1580%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1198%2C%22size%22%3A0%2C%22display%22%3A%22inline%22%2C%22align%22%3A%22left%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Afalse%2C%22bottom%22%3Afalse%7D%2C%22width%22%3A395%2C%22height%22%3A300%7D\"><span data-card-element=\"body\"><span data-card-element=\"center\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7585714285714286\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1400\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border: 0px none;vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;width: 395px;opacity: 1;cursor: zoom-in;transition: opacity 0.3s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.3s ease-in-out;user-select: auto;height: 300px;visibility: visible;\" data-imgfileid=\"100025534\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=70623b6f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FkN3t5R6pdz65sCc9rN2TDsDLYflE4hJu7D5XCJksKxoXM7BW5gJAYoYib1xrSdsEVIhveqREPxPxzrwiaTic1LRk0NJu24MU35436exP8LlvGA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-lake-id=\"aa1099dadae66ef69b677dbb306c3cde\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span data-card-type=\"inline\" data-lake-card=\"image\" data-card-value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fucc.alicdn.com%2Fpic%2Fdeveloper-ecology%2Fnlekadieflg4i_79dad382a3ed4f3f87ab252da61f2f8a.png%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1580%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1198%2C%22size%22%3A0%2C%22display%22%3A%22inline%22%2C%22align%22%3A%22left%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Afalse%2C%22bottom%22%3Afalse%7D%2C%22width%22%3A395%2C%22height%22%3A300%7D\"><span data-card-element=\"body\"><span data-card-element=\"center\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-lake-id=\"9f0b0a430b7d50e84110e369b648653a\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span data-card-type=\"inline\" data-lake-card=\"image\" data-card-value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fucc.alicdn.com%2Fpic%2Fdeveloper-ecology%2Fnlekadieflg4i_d99187597cb844689bc9f130be93d3e5.jpeg%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A4032%2C%22originHeight%22%3A3024%2C%22size%22%3A0%2C%22display%22%3A%22inline%22%2C%22align%22%3A%22left%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Afalse%2C%22bottom%22%3Afalse%7D%2C%22width%22%3A395%2C%22height%22%3A296%7D\"><span data-card-element=\"body\"><span data-card-element=\"center\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1400\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border: 0px none;vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;width: 395px;opacity: 1;cursor: zoom-in;transition: opacity 0.3s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.3s ease-in-out;user-select: auto;height: 296px;visibility: visible;\" data-imgfileid=\"100025535\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=366c8798&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FkN3t5R6pdz6mhPibPHY7CoyUTick6kcn5gsC720OkDX5via6pebaCQwyCO66OicFN3OqSl568efGtFj4vECJq705Roic71h8nobSCqoZ37QbmTKs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-lake-id=\"bef85d25d24cff1cf823fe05ce3ec768\" style=\"margin: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmd2fnp11g4l\">本论文从大规模生产实践出发，直面云原生时代本地存储的核心矛盾：一方面要追求更低时延与更高吞吐，另一方面必须满足云上多租户、可运维、可演进、可用性保障等工程要求。论文给出了清晰的技术路线图与可验证的体系化经验总结，也标志着阿里云在存储基础设施“软硬一体化”探索上获得了国际学术界的高度认可。</span></p>\n  <p data-lake-id=\"335299b3c52c898efb90e6ac21275d77\" style=\"margin: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mmd2fnp1v6j\" style=\"font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;\">论文不仅系统阐述了</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">阿里云本地盘（Local Storage）技术从纯软件到软硬协同的“三代进化史”</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;\">（以咖啡浓度由低到高命名：Espresso、Doppio、Ristretto），更提出了一种</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">前瞻性的端云融合存储架构——Latte</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;\">。该架构通过基于机器学习的 IO 调度（ML IO Dispatcher）与cache准入控制技术（Admission Controller），在更轻量的系统开销下实现</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">更稳定、更接近“极致”的时延与吞吐体验</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;\">。在 AI 大模型推理等新兴场景中，</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Latte 可构建高性能、大容量、高性价比的弹性缓存层</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;\">，有效降低 GPU 等计算资源消耗，提升推理效率与响应速度，为云原生与 AI 负载提供了兼顾性能确定性与资源效率的新工程范式。</span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mmd2kh5lllu\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 33px auto;letter-spacing: 0.578px;visibility: visible;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <div style=\"margin-top: -2px;margin-bottom: -2px;transform: scale(0.9);transform-origin: center center;visibility: visible;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;text-align: center;justify-content: center;visibility: visible;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"margin-right: 10px;margin-left: 10px;display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: center;min-width: 10%;height: auto;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"font-size:29px;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <p><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">01</span></strong></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">阿里云本地盘技术演进与架构变革</span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-lake-id=\"556ae9e8fcf6848dfca1e2e0086c0d89\" style=\"margin: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mmd2fnp11s8q\" style=\"font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;\">论文用“咖啡”隐喻概括本地盘技术不断“提纯”的过程：每一代都围绕瓶颈点做架构级调整，在性能、隔离、可运维性与可演进性之间寻找更优解</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;\">。</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;\">最初，ESPRESSO 通过用户态轮询架构（SPDK）释放 NVMe 性能，却牺牲了 CPU 效率和裸金属支持；随后，DOPPIO 借力 ASIC DPU 卸载虚拟化，提升了隔离与交付能力，但硬件固化难以跟上 SSD 快速迭代，也缺乏对复杂云特性的支持；如今的 RISTRETTO 采用 ASIC 与 ARM SoC 软硬协同设计，既</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">保留高性能数据面</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">，又</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">通过可编程控制面实现灵活的 FTL 与卷管理，已在大规模场景中逼近物理盘性能极限</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mmd2m53xm61\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n    <div data-role=\"paragraph\" data-color=\"#ef7060\" data-id=\"86516\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:-apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0em;\">\n     <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86516\" data-color=\"#ef7060\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin:30px auto;outline:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(20, 20, 220);font-weight:bold;padding-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;line-height:17px;\">\n       <p style=\"outline: 0px;\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">RISTRETTO 架构：</span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-lake-id=\"9c4f53bdbec4b1167fadbe062abd6dd0\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span data-card-type=\"inline\" data-lake-card=\"image\" data-card-value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fucc.alicdn.com%2Fpic%2Fdeveloper-ecology%2Fnlekadieflg4i_a9ee0b06e6ad4830a2ee10b249f00b0